summary: TL* TAKATA RECALL. THE CONTACT OWNS A 2008 JEEP COMMANDER. WHILE DRIVING 60 MPH, THE PASSENGER SIDE AIR BAG DEPLOYED WITHOUT WARNING OR IMPACT. THE CONTACT CALLED LUJACKS NORTHPARK AUTO PLAZA (3700 N HARRISON ST DAVENPORT, IA 52806) AND KIMBERLY CAR CITY (LOCATED AT 625 W DAVENPORT RD DAVENPORT, IA 52806) AND WAS INFORMED BY BOTH DEALERS TO TAKE THE VEHICLE TO AN AUTO BODY SHOP. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED  THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT NOTIFIED. THE VIN WAS UNKNOWN. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 150,071.  UPDATED 08/11/17*LJ     *CN
